{"type": "article", "id": 27552, "title": "单手掌控的过滤器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-31T07:01:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151004bHI7CExDTK4wf3NB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>为了帮助人们在厨房中解放双手，加快料理速度，Equals Design 为厨具品牌 <a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-us/\">Joseph Joseph</a> 设计了一款可以单手掌控的过滤器 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/37362481/Joseph-Joseph-Shake-it-Self-Tapping-Sieve\">Shake-It</a>。它的设计非常简洁，塑料套固定住了过滤器的金属把手，只需要单手摇晃就可以使面粉落下，这个时候你就可以同时进行搅拌了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-us/shake-it\">购买链接</a>，售价为 17 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151001cDV8C6QYgWHE7S5N.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.57777778\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151001CR7JrlQuFxL8AEsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151002LuNi03GWhkAwUJ1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}